oads/2021/12/fourteen-36x24.jpg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/fourteen-48x32.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /> <img class="alignnone wp-image-635318" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/one.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="366" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/one.jpg 1080w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/one-300x200.jpg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/one-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/one-768x511.jpg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/one-24x16.jpg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/one-36x24.jpg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/one-48x32.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /> <img class="alignnone wp-image-635320" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/nine.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="367" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/nine.jpg 1080w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/nine-300x200.jpg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/nine-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/nine-768x512.jpg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/nine-24x16.jpg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/nine-36x24.jpg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/nine-48x32.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /> <img class="alignnone wp-image-635321" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Left-to-right-Mallam-Shehu-Abdulkadir-Ag.-MD-Abuja-Enterprise-Agency-Alhaji-Abdulrazaq-Laramo-ag-Secretary-of-Education-and-representative-of-the-Permanent-Secretary-FCT.jpg" alt="" width="550" 